1. create two arrays each containing half of the previous arrays

2. repeat step 1 until all arrays contain 1 element

3. while array 1 and array 2 have elements do step 4 and 5

4. if the first int in array 1 in lower take it and put it on the end of array 3

5. otherwise take the first int and array 2 put it on the end of array 3

6. while array 1 still has elements do step 7

7. take the first element at the end of array 1 and put it on the end of array 3

8. while array 2 still has elements do step 9

9. take the first element at the end of array 2 and put it on the end of array 3

10. return array 3



